Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 05 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Rupture Lig. scapholunatum' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Dorsal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Central' checkbox is enabled
And 'Palmar' checkbox is enabled

And 'Static SL dissociation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Secondary arthrosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'DISI deformity' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Static SL dissociation' checkbox
Then 'Rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Insufficiency' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Secondary arthrosis' checkbox
Then 'Stage I' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage II' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage III' radio button is enabled
